data.description: Charming, well-appointed 3 bedroom, 2bath, home that backs to National Forest. Special hideaway with huge, covered and cool front porch to enjoy family & friends at this Mountain Chalet in the pines.  Enjoy the elk as they peek over the fence at the vibrant and verdant plant life in the inviting fenced yard.   The 16x16 & 10x12 shed/workshops complement the carport and RV Parking. Abundant custom cabinetry makes the kitchen a dream, while the gas lit heating stove beckons into the large living room.  The light and bright interior is accented with solar tube skylights.  The master suite is alongside the other downstairs bedroom, which is set up as a professional office & hobby room.  Large upstairs bedroom and bath.   Property is an estate and is sold in as-is condition.
